"{\"uid\": \"intermatwrestle.com-articles.html-international-blades-and-snyder-into-the-olympic-semifinals-r99452\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Forgot your password?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 21, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earl Smith  Earl Smith\\u2022August 10, 2024  Friday wasn't the best from an American perspective, but Saturday was a new day and it saw the final three members of the Olympic wrestling squad hit the mat.\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"score\": 0.6036270195754082, \"rank\": 0.4887218045113575, \"text\": \"Earl Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"score\": 0.6036270195754082, \"rank\": 0.4887218045113575, \"text\": \"Earl Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999968632609209, \"rank\": 3.0332923758119008e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of them have advanced to the semifinals later today.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First-time Olympian Kennedy Blades was the first American to take the mat on Saturday and she made sure her debut at 76 kg in women's freestyle was memorable.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999920387381, \"rank\": 7.961048611927832e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 300, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.9999808783341125, \"rank\": 1.9108683117847764e-05, \"text\": \"Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy\"}, {\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999968632609209, \"rank\": 3.0332923758119008e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blades opened up the floodgates early in the opening period as she gained a takedown with a low single.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the first, Blades landed a massive double leg, taking her opponent Catalina Axente (Romania) from feet to back for a 6-0 lead at the break.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Consolidated_PBY_Catalina\", \"score\": 0.9999540325585919, \"rank\": 4.5966018590797027e-05, \"text\": \"Catalina\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Consolidated_PBY_Catalina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Consolidated_PBY_Catalina\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9510147940375092, \"rank\": 0.04304139870324189, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second period, Blades abruptly ended the bout with a beautiful five-point backarch suplex.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The move forced Axente to land on her neck and she was down on the mat being attended to by medical personnel for a lengthy time before leaving the wrestling area on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The quarterfinals saw Blades in a rematch against Cuba's Milaimys Marin Potrille.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.5667102992463978, \"rank\": 0.5046323017486617, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two met a few months ago at the Grand Prix of Spain and Marin Potrille took that bout.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999965676906655, \"rank\": 2.8918336053995304e-06, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only scoring that took place in the opening period was a shot clock violation on Marin Potrille which put Blades up 1-0.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second period saw the Cuban knot up the score at one with an early step-out point.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1296, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.9185018986224331, \"rank\": 0.0887266421456499, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Undeterred, Blades shot Marin Potrille off the mat for a step out of her own and a 2-1 lead.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Blades would extend that lead as she hipped into a double leg attempt from Marin Potrille sending the Cuban to her back for another pair of points.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.9185018986224331, \"rank\": 0.0887266421456499, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the second period, Blades took a half shot which was countered by Marin Potrille bringing the match score to 4-3.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Blades was able to stay out of danger for the rest of the period and took the 4-3 decision and she will move into the semifinals.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the semifinals, Blades will have top-seeded Aiperi Medet Kyzy of Kyrgyzstan.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiperi_Medet_Kyzy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aiperi Medet Kyzy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiperi_Medet_Kyzy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiperi_Medet_Kyzy\"}, {\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\", \"score\": 0.9997426760411763, \"rank\": 0.00025739019166523287, \"text\": \"Kyrgyzstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medet Kyzy is a two-time world medalist who was second in the world in 2023.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyle Snyder's quest for a second Olympic title and third Olympic medal started in a shaky manner as he gave up a four-point throw to China's Awusayiman Habila to start off his tournament.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.8442804931546848, \"rank\": 0.18242790073773607, \"text\": \"Kyle Snyder\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Snyder_(wrestler)\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6106929706679601, \"rank\": 0.6363667414064514, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snyder would enter the second period facing a 4-0 deficit.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second period, Snyder would methodically battle back and chipped away at Habila's lead.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He got on the board early with a snapdown and spin for a takedown, quickly followed by a single leg run out of bounds, which made the score 4-3.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snyder added two more takedowns and surrendered a step-out point which made the final score, 9-5.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a second US vs Cuba quarterfinal Snyder took on Arturo Silot Torres with a spot in the semifinals hanging in the balance.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9967104126715114, \"rank\": 0.0033004293719521758, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2616, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.5667102992463978, \"rank\": 0.5046323017486617, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was little in the way of action in the opening period which led to a shot clock violation on Silot Torres and a point for Snyder.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2851, \"end\": 2857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Action picked up in the second period as Silot Torres took a half-hearted shot in Snyder's direction.\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2942, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American promptly threw Silot Torres to his back and quickly picked up a fall.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2966, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999968632609209, \"rank\": 3.0332923758119008e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The semifinals have a massive matchup in store for Snyder.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3097, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will have 2023 world champion Akhmed Tazhudinov of Bahrain.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3138, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Khan_bin_K\\u00fcch\\u00fck\", \"score\": 0.9999999984297574, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akhmed\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Khan_bin_K\\u00fcch\\u00fck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ahmed_Khan_bin_K\\u00fcch\\u00fck\"}, {\"begin\": 3159, \"end\": 3166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999592276407664, \"rank\": 4.0373420825100916e-05, \"text\": \"Bahrain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahrain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair met in the 2023 world quarterfinals and Tazhudinov shocked Snyder with an 11-0 tech.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999988113593433, \"rank\": 1.172184942154554e-06, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lone American not to advance in the session was Zain Retherford at 65 kg.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999968632609209, \"rank\": 3.0332923758119008e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3315, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zain Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford drew the #2 seed Rahman Amouzad (Iran) in a battle of past world champions.\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3341, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999998411681317, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 3369, \"end\": 3383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahman_Amouzad\", \"score\": 0.9999929510357254, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rahman Amouzad\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahman_Amouzad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahman_Amouzad\"}, {\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999982952045664, \"rank\": 1.7043903875114475e-06, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford was never able to get past the long arms of Amouzad to get a significant offensive attempt.\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3428, \"end\": 3438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999998411681317, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Iranian took the match 8-0 and continued into this afternoon's semifinals.\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\", \"score\": 0.999982979096578, \"rank\": 1.516440987794757e-05, \"text\": \"Iranian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iranian_peoples\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amouzad will face 2023 world champion Iszmail Musukaev (Hungary).\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3667, \"end\": 3674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8112658643163818, \"rank\": 0.2326413962585986, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should Amouzad win, Retherford will be pulled back into repechage.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3697, \"end\": 3707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999998411681317, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no comments to display.\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You need to be a member in order to leave a comment  Sign up for a new account in our community.\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's easy!\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 3887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already have an account?\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign in here.\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Show all categories  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 InterMatPowered by Invision Community\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 4004, \"entities\": []}]}"